function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	--Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idRunestone, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idRunestone, false)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idDummyGizmo)
	
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idRunestone, S_CHARGED_EFFECT)

--	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawnerRandom, true)
--	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawnerRanged, true)
--	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawnerCaster, true)
	
		t_Monsters = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Scos_TheDiviner_Monsters_01")

	for i = 1, #t_Monsters do

		if Hydra.ActorIsAlive(t_Monsters[i]) then
			Hydra.ActorKill(t_Monsters[i])
		end
	end

function Start(listValidActors, idActorDetector)

	-- Checks to see if a player is within the trigger volume and has the Hazel-Witch Ley Buff so
	-- it unhides the runestone and makes it interactable.
	-- Its giving a count for the number of valid players here too

	nPlayer = 0

	for u, idActor in pairs(listValidActors) do

		if Hydra.ActorIsPlayer(idActor) then
			
			nPlayer = nPlayer + 1
			
			bHasBuff = Hydra.BuffIsOnActor(sPower, idBuff, idActor)
			
			if bHasBuff then
				Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idRunestone, false)
				Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idRunestone, false)
				
				bBuffedPlayerInTrigger = true
				break
			else
				bBuffedPlayerInTrigger = false
			end
		end
	end
	
	
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idRunestone, true)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idRunestone, true)
	
	bBuffedPlayerInTrigger = false
	
	nPlayer = nPlayer - 1
end

function Start(flGameTime)

	if bBuffedPlayerInTrigger == true then
		nCounter = nCurrentCount
		UF_SpawnWaves()
	end

end

-- Core Vars
-- //////////////////////////////////////////// --

sPower = Hydra.ReferencePower("QST_Scos_TheDiviner_RunestoneDetection")
idBuff = "RUNESTONE_DETECT_BUFF"

idThisQuest = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

idRunestone = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idThisQuest, "Runestone")[1]
idDummyGizmo = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idThisQuest, "DummyGizmo")[1]

idSpawnerRandom = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idThisQuest, "SpawnerRandom")[1]
idSpawnerRanged = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idThisQuest, "SpawnerRanged")[1]
idSpawnerCaster = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idThisQuest, "SpawnerCaster")[1]

nPlayer = 0
nCounter = 0
nCurrentCount = 0

-- ///////////////////////////////////////////// --
-- Setup invisibility

Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idRunestone, true)
Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(idDummyGizmo, true)

Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idRunestone, true)
